        crm:P3_has_note           "Microservices (ARTEMIS WP9 Task 9.2) emulating virtual IoT sensors distributed across digital models of heritage sites. Generate synthetic environmental data streams (temperature, humidity) based on configurable probabilistic distributions and geographic parameters. Simulate both individual sensors and large clusters, supporting scenario testing and system validation before deployment of any physical sensor hardware." ;
